reater profits to the firm and inflate their bonuses in the years – an investigation conducted by the isa concluded with psagot agreeing to pay a fine of nis0 million as part of a plea bargain0 psagot ceo at the time roy vermus was subsequently compelled to resign from the firm after the supreme court rejected an appeal he filed against his forced ouster from the company see alsoedit economy of israel venture capital in israel referencesedit  gewirtz jason  february 0 israels business elite weigh irans nuclear threat cnbc retrieved  february 0   contact us psagot investment house retrieved  february 0   psagot group – israel’s largest investment house duns  retrieved  february 0   a b bergman roee  december  ravid silbiger quit psagot ofek globes retrieved  march 0   dagan ram  november  york capital buys leumis psagot ofek haaretz retrieved  february 0   rochvarger michael  october  apax takeover of psagot falls apart haaretz retrieved  february 0   psagot buyout boosts private equity total to twoyear high globes  february 0 retrieved  march 0   a b peer eran  december  roy vermus leaves psagot globes retrieved  march 0   hazani golan raz hadar  september  אני לא מבין איך מנכל בית השקעות יכול להיות רגוע i dont understand how the ceo of an investment firm can stay relaxed calcalist in hebrew retrieved  march 0 ורמוס קיבל לידיו את בית ההשקעות ב־ כשהיה בן  בלבד   magen hadas  january  antitrust authority approves prismapsagot deal globes retrieved  march 0   stein ron  january  psagot buys first major pension fund globes retrieved  march 0   bindman raheli  january 0 בלעדי לכלכליסט פסגות מוכרת את מלון ארבל בטבריה ב מיליון שקל exclusive to calcalist psagot sells arbel hotel in tiberias for nis million calcalist in hebrew retrieved  march 0 בית ההשקעות פסגות מוכר את בית המלון ארבל בטבריה שנרכש על ידי קרן הפנסיה הותיקה העל קרן הפנסיה של הסתדרות העובדים הלאומית אותה רכש פסגות לפני כעשרה חודשים   avriel eytan  september  the man who wanted to ground the executive jets haar